{
  "stem": "21013.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And because I had been raised with maids and I didn't know anything-- I didn't know how to iron.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't know how to scrub a floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they thought I was very stupid and very useless.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she said that people like me should be eliminated, because I was just a useless creature.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I was so miserable and so unhappy--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember her name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All I know is I didn't speak English at the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the few weeks that I was there, I went to bed with a dictionary every night just so that I could learn enough to tell her what I thought of her.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I escaped by squeezing myself out through a toilet window.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had a little diamond ring that I gave to a greengrocer across the street so he gave me carfare.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went to the Jewish Refugees Committee and I saw Miss Fellner after waiting for hours, all in my uniform because I had to wear a uniform.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And said, I'd rather go back to Vienna and go to a concentration camp than stay in that nursery, because it's just like a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, now that I'm used to scrubbing and cleaning, it wouldn't be so bad.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But at that time, I just felt terrible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was alone and I didn't speak English.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And all the other young nurses put all the dirty work on me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And everybody was making fun of me because I didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she then turned me over to the Society of Friends, the Quakers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they found me a foster home in the country, because they wanted to get me out of London by then.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
